#  CLANG_LIBRARY_DIR           - Where to find Clang libraries
#
#  CLANG_CLANG_LIB             - LibClang library
#  CLANG_CLANGFRONTEND_LIB     - Clang Frontend Library
#  CLANG_CLANGDRIVER_LIB       - Clang Driver Library
